Reviews/Synopsis
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
No matter what you think of Britney from her private life to her shows or her music, this is the ultimate way to see her. This collection moves from the most recent "My Perogative" all the way back to her first hit "Baby One More Time". Each video looks incredible, and there are even alternate versions and hidden footage throughout to keep you entertained for hours. The sound mix is a very strong stereo (oddly not 5.1 surround). She's a pioneer in the visual medium, and this collection proves how very strong she is in the music video. It's a stunning collection that represents the best of her career in one convenient package.
